name: Innovation and commercialization initiative program; establishment
text:
INNOVATION AND COMMERCIALIZATION INITIATIVE PROGRAM
 
Note
 
  Subpart repealed June 30, 2021.  L 2017, c 39, §3.
 
         [See Note at subpart heading.]  There is established within the University of Hawaii an innovation and commercialization initiative program under the direction of the vice president for research and innovation. [L 2017, c 39, pt of §2]
